<chapter title="Card relationship properties">
    <section title="Introduction">
    	<p>Card relationship properties allow users to create a relationship between cards. For example, users can make a defect to connect to a story. This can be changed to another story or bug as needed.</p>
		<screenshot src="resources/images/card_relationship_prop.png"/>
		<p>where 'Depend on' is a card relationship property which points to story card '#1 Navigate to and read Email' as its value.</p>
    </section>

